<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV57">
<l>pulakkuṇ ṭalappuṇṭa rīkatta pōrkkoṇṭai valliyoṉṟāl</l>
<l>vilakkuṇ ṭulākiṉṟu vēlviḻik kiṉṟaṉa kaṇṇaṉkaiyāl</l>
<l>malakkuṇ ṭamutañ curanta maṟikaṭal pōṉṟavaṟṟāl</l>
<l>kalakkuṇṭa nāṉṟukaṇ ṭāremmai yāruṅ kaḻaṟalarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] senses roam, being blocked by one creeper with a tuft heaped with</l>
<l>lotus [and] earrings. Spear [eyes]s open. None who has seen [us] the time we</l> 
<l>were agitaged by those, being like the receding ocean from which gushes forth</l>
<l>the ambrosia churned by the hands of Kaṇṇaṉ, will grumble with us.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
